Developed by Ottavio Manno: ottomanh@me.com

Version 1.0
(Windows Only)

Usage:

1) Place the script where are located the directories to compress or everywhere if you prefer to put a custom path

2) Launch the script and follow the instruction in the terminal

3) A directory called zipped will be created in the script root with the directories compressed

Optional features

* To insert a credit file in every archive create a file called 'Readme.txt' in the script root
